NAME:
   rockamalgcli.test amalg - Amalgamates Lua files with all dependencies inside one Lua file.

USAGE:
   rockamalgcli.test amalg [command options] firmware

DESCRIPTION:
   The firmware should be a single Lua file or directory with main.lua and other Lua files.
   
   The dependencies file should be in the Luarocks format.
   
   See the tutorial https://developers.enapter.com/docs/tutorial/lua-complex/multi-file to learn more.

OPTIONS:
   --deps value, -d value      Use dependencies file
   --rockspec value, -r value  Use rockspec file for dependencies
   --output value, -o value    Output firmware file name
   --help, -h                  show help (default: false)
   
